00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:13.700
Joe: The next question I've got here is,
Question: "How much money can I make doing

00:00:13.700 --> 00:00:14.700
what you teach?

00:00:14.700 --> 00:00:18.250
How long will it take me to start making money?"

00:00:18.250 --> 00:00:24.490
Joe: The "Millionaire Matrix", the way I've
outlined it, and some of you have seen it

00:00:24.490 --> 00:00:27.770
in some of my other material and some of you
haven't, but the way I outline it is I show

00:00:27.770 --> 00:00:34.050
you how, by doing one deal a month, you can
be a millionaire in two years; just by doing

00:00:34.050 --> 00:00:36.129
one deal a month, you can make a million dollars.

00:00:36.129 --> 00:00:38.590
So, it's not that difficult to make it happen.

00:00:38.590 --> 00:00:43.870
Joe: Now, realistically, as far as cash flow
goes, to be able to make $100,000 to $150,000

00:00:43.870 --> 00:00:47.809
your fist year in the business -- we've got
people who do it all the time.

00:00:47.809 --> 00:00:53.320
I've got students that make 4, 5, 6 or $700,000
a year cash flow in this business.

00:00:53.320 --> 00:00:57.429
I've got other students that make 0 and they
never do their first deal.

00:00:57.429 --> 00:01:00.559
But the people that aren't making money are
people that aren't doing the deals.

00:01:00.559 --> 00:01:05.050
Joe: I also have people that are struggling
because there are certain things that they

00:01:05.050 --> 00:01:07.460
have to learn that they haven't learned yet.

00:01:07.460 --> 00:01:11.040
They have to learn how to communicate properly
with people and they have to learn how to

00:01:11.040 --> 00:01:13.410
take action on the things that they learn.

00:01:13.410 --> 00:01:17.460
Joe: If you learn those things, you can make
an awful lot of money in this business.

00:01:17.460 --> 00:01:23.000
You can make millions of dollars, plus, you'll
learn how to, if you're like some of my students

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:28.000
-- I have one student, Nina Lance, who right
now owns 60 properties where she is keeping

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:32.800
them long term as well as having cash flow
from them every month, and she's doing deals

00:01:32.800 --> 00:01:35.690
that they're flipping every month so they're
making cash flow from that as well.

00:01:35.690 --> 00:01:38.860
So, there's a lot of different sources of
income that you can make from the different

00:01:38.860 --> 00:01:39.860
things that I'm teaching.

00:01:39.860 --> 00:01:43.110
Joe: You just need to start somewhere though;
you need to get your first deal done.

00:01:43.110 --> 00:01:46.690
You need to get over that hump, and that's
what the Mentor Program is about -- to get

00:01:46.690 --> 00:01:49.310
you over the hump, to help you to understand
that, "Yes, I can do this.'

00:01:49.310 --> 00:01:53.750
Joe: For some of you that are more advanced
that are thinking about the program, what

00:01:53.750 --> 00:01:56.860
we can do for you is probably working on a
much higher level.

00:01:56.860 --> 00:02:04.951
The more you know, the more valuable this
program will be to you, because there are

00:02:04.951 --> 00:02:08.580
tweaks in here -- just one small tweak can
make a huge difference to your business; it

00:02:08.580 --> 00:02:12.159
can double or triple your income in a very
short period of time.

00:02:12.159 --> 00:02:18.239
And, we can also help you build your business
so that it turns into passive income after

00:02:18.239 --> 00:02:19.890
a period of years.

00:02:19.890 --> 00:02:22.890
I hope that helps.

00:02:22.890 --> 00:02:31.280
Talk to you soon.

